{"tid":13294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西足球隊包機墜毀71死6生還 門將須截肢求生","createTime":"2016-11-30T03:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T13:00:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b76dfaf90fb2eb850e42295286b39ff335c8098","tid":13294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"巴西甲級聯賽足球俱樂部查比高恩斯（Chapecoense）前往哥倫比亞參加南美盃決賽的包機，二十九日不幸墜機，機上乘客和機組人員共七十七人僅有六人生還，包括五名球員，但獲救的門將丹尼洛（Marcos Danilo Padilha）送醫後不治。目前所有南美盃賽程全面延後。原本球隊要直飛前往，但巴西民航局未批准直飛，改從玻利維亞轉機，結果不幸發生憾事。 <br />\n<br />\n赴南美盃決賽 摔落哥倫比亞 <br />\n查比高恩斯足球隊二十七日才結束與新科巴西盃冠軍寶梅拉斯（palmeiras）的最後廝殺賽，二十七日便包機由聖保羅出發，於玻利維亞轉機前往哥倫比亞，準備參加三十日的南美盃決賽，卻不幸在巴西時間二十九日凌晨一點十五分，在目的地美德殷（Medelin）附近山區墜機。 <br />\n這架編號CP2933的美里達航空公司（LaMia）包機，從玻利維亞中部聖克魯斯的維魯維魯機場起飛，登機名單共八十一人，包括七十二名乘客和九名機組人員，但該球隊總理皮利尼歐（Plinio David de Nes Filho）等四人並未登機，空位是否補實則不得而知。"},{"pid":"53297a537302e500fd778e28c46da56cdae785c4","tid":13294,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:56:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1baf4bb657da94c887f19389caffd82ea1470fa","tid":13294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2016/new/nov/30/images/bigPic/600_304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2016%2Fnew%2Fnov%2F30%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F600_304.jpg&h=8adfd9b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://sports.now.com/sport/news/1/541/16682173541/16692371879_600x397.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F1%2F541%2F16682173541%2F16692371879_600x397.jpg&h=04d865f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n查比高恩斯球隊發言人表示，24歲的佛曼（Jackson Follmann）雖從空難幸運生還，但必須進行截肢手術：「佛曼動了部分手術，一條腿被截肢了，但他沒事。」同時生還的球隊後衛納多（Helio Neto）則必須進行顱內手術，另一名後衛魯斯切爾（Alan Ruschel）傷勢穩定但仍須待在加護病房進行治療。"},{"pid":"d46e8b295d3b774ae107f450346e9d74c206a296","tid":13294,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d4db2b199da3161ad44a4e9fdc043a47f21852","tid":13294,"uid":13433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/115818_49de9347e959188e97544defd7546a4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F115818_49de9347e959188e97544defd7546a4d.jpg&h=646d0066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到依張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117d24110fa3122f2dade393dfbe10a939a52bc6","tid":13294,"uid":27831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea3175d632181f3047328ff206581864c2a98da","tid":13294,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de642ff3a6bc4233d3df73c38f766f334b07812","tid":13294,"uid":41967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e48d033964217a2d906bd02e25df3e6d5fbce02","tid":13294,"uid":56,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e966e7bab3dcbbbf3b073adae5e146f617820644","tid":13294,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif